Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管今天还是明天  希望能和大家幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然预先穿好泳衣是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OPC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:33.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}ジャージの女の子 何か持ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:33.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿着线衫的女孩  身边带着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.75,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}チャックを外したら 何にでもなれるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}解下衣服的拉链  便成百变之身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:46.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}大切なこと探して 海の底にも行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:46.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}追寻重要的事情  海底也能前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:53.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}高まり長すぎ リボンを解ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:53.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}解开那高高扎起的长丝带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:05.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}すぐ会いに行くよ 君の非常サインが 呼んでくれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:05.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}马上就去见你哦  如果你那特别印记将我召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:13.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}廻り出せ 運命を書き換えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:13.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开始轮转  重写命运之书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:21.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}飛び出せ Fly away on the try again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:21.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跳出禁锢  Fly away on the try again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:27.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}舌を出し踏み出す危険なラフ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:27.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}俏皮吐舌踏上危险的不毛之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:36.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}燃えてくる Fly away try unite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:36.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尽情燃烧  Fly away try unite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:51.66,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(947,107)\fade(652,563)}欢迎来到鸭川！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在上学的路上  我发现有个女孩溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问你穿成这样是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上了岸之后发现我的衣服都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老师请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一直都准备这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带～着～的～话～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才消防局来了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救得那个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说没有大碍并已经恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然这么说实在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  几点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候有空都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长不管怎样都说非你不可  真是吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要做学生会长的练习对象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.03,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱取り：原文乱取り是指练习柔道的方法之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线衫部还是那么忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美千要入部吗  还在招收部员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  今天你没穿校服上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来的时候给弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人还真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的吗  但是我们还是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么遥远的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么换场地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  超级可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿校服的前辈也很棒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  其实这个是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  在大赛前得到了很好的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你要是能继承学生会或是剑道部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就完美收场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也是其他社团的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待您获得三连霸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这蕾丝如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京乃圆同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人在干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线衫部终于有新人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气可嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年没见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停  停  停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是健康的女高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把内裤脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  看够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆  喜欢鸭川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一辈子生活在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么这样问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生了什么马上联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直站在那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你对这个感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fade(100,100)}线衫部  什么事情都会伸出援手  部员一直在招募中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  加入线衫部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天遇见的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得我可以和你好好相处下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意送来校服这份亲切的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及一直为了急救而时刻准备的这身泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是校服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行任务时有义务一直穿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识等级好高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想要不要叫你同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有相同的志向一起前行的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在这词已经不怎么说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家姐姐很喜欢这个词  所以不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的词呢  同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我成为同志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困扰的时候一定会互相帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砰  就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  咱们就当同志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫芬恩·爱·路德·丝·拉芬蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的名字吗  真像外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我兰就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫京乃圆  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  部里终于有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点仓促  同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我现在有些困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  不管是什么事我都会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你驾驶机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗比之德梅特里奥更加深蓝闪耀的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.81,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德梅特里奥：惑星名，本作的敌势力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是我们的目标之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要做的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷加利特的家伙可能在附近潜藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.85,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷加利特：本作己方的外星人势力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不管何时都能出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做好欧比特的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.30,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧比特：萝卜的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候办到基里乌斯你指挥我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球像是曾经毁灭过一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉卡奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:11.79,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉卡奥：德梅特里奥的王女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上竟然还有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是驶过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驶过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西难道是船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆  我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  小圆在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧　奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会让小圆和机器人什么的扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈的堂妹到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是　机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是更加像　这－样－子－
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是有见过这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是　怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德梅特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一批敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷前方7000米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰准备迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前应该和这个机体有过契约
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论何时  都互相敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为同志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…同志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人认为这机体有十分强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰　你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奉雷加利特之命保护你和那个机体的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人？  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是是是～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那边那个管家说可以了为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊佐　难道是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊佐　这么说  那个是阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只会骑自行车而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控都由我们这边来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要进入机体就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要进去就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不照做的话　兰会很为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候来的鸭川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还完全不知道鸭川是个多么好的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  回答只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说　刚才那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是　什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就　就在那个刚才飞起来的机体里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的状态怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于相当亢奋的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打开麦克风吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之一切都在我们的控制之下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉舰队无论发生什么事都不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不像某个人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲着这边来  是要直接上撞过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  谁能回答一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能自己操作的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉　真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能打破亚空间防护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是　传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯：本作三台主角机的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道也挺好玩的　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过　要真玩的话　还是来这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1　2  3……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:02.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}Try 諦めない心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:02.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}Try  永不放弃的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:11.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}この胸の中に 忘れないから いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:11.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}会一直埋藏于我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:16.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}Don't cry きっと約束よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:16.86,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}Don't cry  这是彼此的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:24.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}一人で泣いたりしないで いつだって一緒だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:24.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}一起共同进退  没必要独自流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:35.06,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}悲しみ一つ そっと分けあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:35.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}只有能互相分担悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:39.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}もっと強くなれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:39.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}就能够变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:47.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}今すぐ笑って My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:47.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}马上绽放笑容吧  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:55.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}誰かのためじゃなくて 自分で決めた気持ちだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:55.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}从心底笑出来  不必为谁而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}真っ直ぐな声で Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}用最真挚的声音说Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:12.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}唄ってよいつもの歌 一粒の勇気を心に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:12.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}唱出那首一直以来给内心带来勇气的歌

Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　完事了完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰　想去吃点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河烧  鸭川的酱汁  房总寿司什么的也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:26.26,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fs28}さんが焼き：{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs32}鸭川所在房总半岛的乡土铁板烧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃爱妻便当
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么爱妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是　不对　绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之叫老爸给你做顿大餐就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.74,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fade(438,0)\pos(220,683)}鸭川战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是谁